ain and can cause similar symptoms.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.029045,0.046943,0.061822,0.076446,0.085926,0.097385,0.10654,0.10829,0.11212,0.11759,0.096277,0.06162],"unified_progress":[0.038009,0.064838,0.061413,0.093398,0.10177,0.10069,0.10493,0.10339,0.09862,0.092929,0.078299,0.061713]},{"section":20,"text":"But wait, let's consider the whole picture again.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.11178,0.08986,0.083825,0.075782,0.076789,0.079099,0.081791,0.090336,0.081202,0.055878,0.058797,0.11487],"unified_progress":[0.20362,0.07702,0.064178,0.064294,0.073688,0.073131,0.1031,0.082422,0.078863,0.062913,0.058403,0.058368]},{"section":21,"text":"The combination of high fever, prostration, and those specific eye symptoms makes me wonder if it's something even more severe.","dimension":8,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.030348,0.050368,0.062604,0.071914,0.078174,0.084863,0.092817,0.096704,0.10279,0.116,0.12494,0.08848],"unified_progress":[0.039107,0.063387,0.056659,0.080197,0.0923,0.092598,0.10737,0.10088,0.10095,0.098956,0.092761,0.07484]},{"section":22,"text":"Could it be Tolosa-Hunt syndrome?","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.018526,0.040435,0.057756,0.073094,0.085501,0.09829,0.11002,0.11766,0.12357,0.1259,0.097014,0.052228],"unified_progress":[0.027645,0.05757,0.075989,0.087173,0.094321,0.098982,0.1026,0.10449,0.10131,0.1003,0.085945,0.063668]},{"section":23,"text":"No, that's more about headaches and ophthalmoplegia without the fever and optic disc issues.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.020351,0.032637,0.045215,0.057883,0.071721,0.087655,0.10419,0.11851,0.13133,0.13912,0.11997,0.071421],"unified_progress":[0.031962,0.053461,0.069333,0.079499,0.09072,0.099169,0.10101,0.10598,0.10599,0.10756,0.091079,0.064242]},{"section":24,"text":"Let's go back to cavernous sinus thrombosis.","dimension":5,"group":8,"is_degene